parameters.name: START_TIME
parameters.description:
Start time (SCET) of the instrument cycle in which
    the accumulation occurred.
    The time string is of the form yyyy-dddThh:mm:ss.sssZ. The
    representation of Jan 01, 2000, 00:00:00.000 would be 
    2000-001T00:00:00.000Z.

parameters.name: SCLK
parameters.description:
Binary count of the corrected spacecraft clock's RIM
    and MOD91 counters. The SCLK string is of the form rrrrrrrr:mm.
